snippet.title: Total War: Shogun 2 - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for Total War: Shogun 2 with the official game launch trailer. Watch gameplay and get a small preview of just how epic the battles in this RTS truly are. 


IGN's YouTube is just a taste of our content. Get more:
